1. On je nosio džon* u zelenoj boji. (He was wearing a jacket in green color.)
2. Ona je odlučila da nosi džon* umesto kaputa. (She decided to wear a jacket instead of a coat.)
3. Ona je obukla džon* pre nego što je izašla van. (She put on a jacket before going outside.)
4. Mogu da ti poklonim džon* koju sam kupila. (I can give you the jacket that I bought.)
5. Prošle godine on je kupio džon* sa krznom. (Last year he bought a jacket with fur.)